definitions.definition: A small piece of plastic, metal, ivory, etc., for plucking the strings of a guitar , lyre , mandolin , etc.
A projection of bone or other stiff tissue, such as the ridges in some insects' stridulatory organs.

main_definition: ( music ) A small piece of plastic, metal, ivory, etc., for plucking the strings of a guitar , lyre , mandolin , etc.
secondary_definitions: ( anatomy , zoology ) A projection of bone or other stiff tissue, such as the ridges in some insects' stridulatory organs.
